text:
I'm always up for adding more Alberto Gonzalez to this list. He's up there with the best composers on older hardware.

I was at the mall today and I heard a Christmas song and saw decorations. They waste no time once Halloween is over. Looking outside, I can feel the great holiday magic: cold rain, everyone has a cough and looks tired. I definitely want to build a snowman right now with the nonexistent snow. By the time it actually starts snowing, we'll already have a Christmas music overdose.
